            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Oskar, do you have a minute?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, sure. What do you need?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Well..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Huh..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "So that's what I need. Do you know something about any of the materials Plachta mentioned?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I know what \"Haze Grass\" is. I'm actually growing it now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x26,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Wait, really!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x28,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Um, Oskar? Would it be okay to have some of those flowers?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Well, if you insist that you need them... But they aren't going to bloom at this rate."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Huh? What do you mean?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "\"Haze Grass\" requires a huge amount of nutrients to grow flowers."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I'm giving it my special fertilizer, but it shows no signs of blooming at all."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I didn't know... Oh, maybe."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Maybe if I made some fertilizer with alchemy, it would grow flowers?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Don't know... I've never tried that. I guess we'd have to test it to find out."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Okay, I'll go make the fertilizer. If it grows flowers, you'll share with me, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x3,
            "name_id": 0x3,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, I guess I have no choice. I want to see it bloom, after all."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Thank you, Oskar! Just wait a little while!"
        }
    ]
}